title: 2019 Mediterranean Athletics U23 Indoor Championships
text: The 2019 <a href="Mediterranean%20Athletics%20U23%20Championships">Mediterranean Athletics U23 Indoor Championships</a> was an <a href="athletics%20%28sport%29">athletics</a> competition which was held in <a href="Miramas">Miramas</a>, <a href="France">France</a>, 19 January 2019. A total of 16 events were contested, of which 8 by male and 8 by female athletes.
